         <div type="edition">
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Feasts">
               <label>Chants for the office for the vigils and for selected holy days (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ዋዜማ፡ ዘሰናበት፡ ወዘበዓላት።</foreign>)</label>
